snippet.title: G30 - A Memory Maze (Store Trailer)
snippet.description:
https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/g30/id1184935724?mt=8

Multiple Awards winning game that creates brand new forms of gameplay and player experience and recreates the process of memorizing in unique and innovative mix of telescopic text and graphical puzzle.
The project also has a social narrative function to tell the story of a person with a cognitive disorder and social problems that appear with it.

https://twitter.com/quadrohead
https://www.facebook.com/G30game
http://g30game.com/
